&lt;p&gt;Applications are invited for the post of Band C Specialist Paediatric dentist at the Sheffield Teaching Hospitals NHS Foundation Trust. This post will be based in the community dental service and working in the hospital based paediatric department.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Band C dentist will work in partnership with the wider community dental services team and will focus on the provision of specialist paediatric care for the residents of Sheffield and surrounding areas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Should any further vacancies arise, shortlisted candidates will be considered.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Sheffield Teaching Hospitals NHS Trust promotes Equality of opportunity and Diversity within the workplace&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
